<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="162" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[189,303,1666,1692]" box="[189,303,1666,1692]" pageId="4" pageNumber="162">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,303,1666,1692]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="4" pageNumber="162" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,303,1666,1692]" pageId="4" pageNumber="162">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[188,1399,1712,1914]" pageId="4" pageNumber="162">
This species was described from 
<collectingCountry box="[598,713,1712,1738]" name="Tajikistan" pageId="4" pageNumber="162">Tajikistan</collectingCountry>
and was subsequently recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[1182,1317,1713,1739]" name="Kyrgyzstan" pageId="4" pageNumber="162">Kyrgyzstan</collectingCountry>
in the subalpine (
<quantity box="[317,409,1747,1774]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.555" pageId="4" pageNumber="162" unit="m" value="2555.0">2555 m</quantity>
) and alpine (
<quantity box="[563,655,1748,1774]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.207" pageId="4" pageNumber="162" unit="m" value="3207.0">3207 m</quantity>
) zones (
<bibRefCitation author="Sychevskaya V. I. &amp; Vtorov P. P." box="[753,1158,1747,1774]" pageId="4" pageNumber="162" pagination="518 - 527" refId="ref7699" refString="Sychevskaya V. I. &amp; Vtorov P. P. 1969. Synanthropic flies (Diptera) from mountain Kirghizia. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie 48: 816 - 830. [In Russian, with English summary. English translation in Entomological Review: 48: 518 - 527.]" type="journal article" year="1969">Sychevskaya &amp; Vtorov 1969: 821</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Sychevskaya V. I." pageId="4" pageNumber="162" pagination="498 - 505" refId="ref7651" refString="Sychevskaya V. I. 1970. Zonal distribution of coprophilous and necrophilous flies (Diptera) in Middle Asia. Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie 49: 819 - 831. [Russian, with English summary. English translation in Entomological Review 49: 498 - 505.]" type="journal article" year="1970">Sychevskaya 1970: 827</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Pont A. C." box="[250,421,1783,1809]" pageId="4" pageNumber="162" pagination="57 - 215" refId="ref6887" refString="Pont A. C. 1986. Family Muscidae. In: Soos A. &amp; Papp L. (eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Diptera 11, Scathophagidae - Hypodermatidae: 57 - 215. Akademiai Kiado, Budapest." type="book chapter" year="1986">Pont 1986: 71</bibRefCitation>
). These identifications, made by ACP over fifty years ago and before the radiation of this genus in Asia was even suspected, and almost certainly based only on females, are very probably incorrect. Males of this group of species from 
<collectingCountry box="[743,878,1854,1880]" name="Kyrgyzstan" pageId="4" pageNumber="162">Kyrgyzstan</collectingCountry>
are needed before a definitive name can be provided for these females.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[189,618,264,337]" pageId="5" pageNumber="163" type="distribution">
