<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,342,264,290]" pageId="5" pageNumber="163">Distribution</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[189,618,311,337]" box="[189,618,311,337]" pageId="5" pageNumber="163">
Palaearctic: 
<collectingCountry box="[333,451,311,337]" name="Tajikistan" pageId="5" pageNumber="163">Tajikistan</collectingCountry>
,? 
<collectingCountry box="[473,614,311,337]" name="Kyrgyzstan" pageId="5" pageNumber="163">Kyrgyzstan</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
